    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 for a Class II CPB device. The CFD hemolysis prediction model is accepted as sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for regulatory submission. This assessment has been applied in clinical research contexts to support device design decisions.",
